   <p style="margin-bottom:5.000000pt;margin-top:5.000000pt"><span style="font-size:12pt">Фиолетовый</span></p>
   <p style="margin-bottom:5.000000pt;margin-top:5.000000pt"><span style="font-size:12pt">Мужчина</span></p>
   <p style="margin-bottom:5.000000pt;margin-top:5.000000pt"><span style="font-size:12pt">Девушка</span></p>
